point to
  a number of instances over the past year where papers I have submitted =
have
  been editorially rejected prior to peer review because I have included =
too
  many citations<st1:PersonName w:st=3D"on">,</st1:PersonName> forcing a =
pruning
  that some might interpret as a either deliberate omission or a case of
  &quot;amnesia<st1:PersonName =
w:st=3D"on">.</st1:PersonName>&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><font size=3D1 color=3Dblack face=3DVerdana><span
  =
